entry.value: select * from table where field is not null

SELECT "Passenger_ID", CAST((("Passenger_ID" * "Passenger_ID") * 73) % 900000 + 100000 AS INTEGER) AS "Passenger_Key", CASE WHEN (CURRENT_DATE - CAST("DOB" AS DATE)) / 365 < 13 THEN 'Child' WHEN (CURRENT_DATE - CAST("DOB" AS DATE)) / 365 BETWEEN 13 AND 19 THEN 'Young Adult' WHEN (CURRENT_DATE - CAST("DOB" AS DATE)) / 365 BETWEEN 20 AND 39 THEN 'Adult' WHEN (CURRENT_DATE - CAST("DOB" AS DATE)) / 365 BETWEEN 40 AND 59 THEN 'Middle-Aged' ELSE 'Senior' END AS "Age_Category", ((CURRENT_DATE - CAST("DOB" AS DATE)) / 365)::INTEGER AS "Age", "Gender", occupation, nationality, city, country, CURRENT_DATE as "Start_Date", '9999-12-31'::DATE as "End_Date", "IS_INSERTED", "IS_MODIFIED" as "Last_Updated", membership_status, loyalty_tier FROM passenger WHERE "IS_MODIFIED" > '${last_extraction_time:isNull():ifElse('1970-01-01 00:00:00',${last_extraction_time})}' OR "IS_INSERTED" > '${last_extraction_time:isNull():ifElse('1970-01-01 00:00:00',${last_extraction_time})}' ORDER BY GREATEST("IS_MODIFIED", "IS_INSERTED")
